<p>As Google continues to expand AI Overviews, this trend is expected to grow, further cutting into organic traffic and making traditional SEO tactics less effective.</p>
<p>Plus, AI Overviews now show for <a href="https://www.searchenginejournal.com/study-google-ai-overviews-appear-in-47-of-search-results/535096/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">47%</a> of searches‚Äîmost of those informational‚Äîbut with the potential to spread to other types in the future.</p>
<p>But it‚Äôs not all bad news. While AI Overviews are changing the game, they‚Äôre also creating new opportunities for brands that know how to adapt. Google‚Äôs market share is still <a href="https://sparktoro.com/blog/new-research-google-search-grew-20-in-2024-receives-373x-more-searches-than-chatgpt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">around 90%</a>, and search volume grew by 21% in 2024 (four times ChatGPT‚Äôs total search volume).</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/growth-of-desktop-google-search-2023-2024-datos-sparktoro.webp" alt="growth of desktop google searches from 2023 to 2024 from sparktoro" width="1280" height="720" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-91578" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/growth-of-desktop-google-search-2023-2024-datos-sparktoro.webp 1280w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/growth-of-desktop-google-search-2023-2024-datos-sparktoro-980x551.webp 980w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/growth-of-desktop-google-search-2023-2024-datos-sparktoro-480x270.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) 1280px, 100vw" /></p>
